üëâ Rule: All checked exceptions extend Exception but NOT RuntimeException.

‚úÖ 5. LIST OF ALL RUNTIME (UNCHECKED) EXCEPTIONS ‚Äî FULL LIST (IMPORTANT)

Compiler does NOT force handling.

‚úî Arithmetic problems

